---
// src/components/Section9FullProgramOverview.astro
const programIncludes = [
    "The Pulse Cascade Splitter for breaking down reference tracks",
    "Our AI Chord Progression Analyzer for professional harmony",
    "Coaching from our team of active industry professionals",
    "Custom resources tailored to your specific genre and goals",
    "A community of serious producers at your level",
    "Connections to industry professionals who can advance your career"
];
---
<section id="program-overview" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#070710] to-[#0a0a16] px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight pb-1">
            <span class="block text-silvery-gradient">If We're a Good Fit:</span>
            <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pop-pink to-brand-blue">What Working Together Looks Like</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400">
            Pulse Academy is a serious investment for serious producers. We offer different tiers based on your goals and how hands-on you want the coaching to be.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glassmorphism p-6 md:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-silvery-gradient mb-6 text-center pb-1">Our program includes:</h3>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4 list-none">
            {programIncludes.map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start text-gray-300">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pop-teal mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                    {item}
                </li>
            ))}
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-8 prose prose-invert prose-md max-w-none text-gray-300 text-center">
            <p>For those wanting hands-on mentorship, our higher tier includes one-on-one coaching, custom vocals, professional stem mastering, and our industry contact "black book."</p>
            <p>For self-driven producers, we offer comprehensive group coaching, full access to our technology, and regular feedback on your music.</p>
            <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-100">We'll discuss specific options and pricing during your Instant Song Upgrade session if it seems like we'd be a good fit for each other.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section> 